{"segment_id": "00371", "page_num": 371, "segment": "Bottom Line\n\nUnlike a traditional e-commerce company, you don’t have a lot of control\nover inventory and listings. But what you do have is insight into what is\nselling well, so you can go and get more like it. If you find that a particular\nproduct category, geographic region, house size, or color is selling well, you\ncan encourage those sellers---and find more like them.\n\nCHAPter 27: two-SIDeD MArKetPLACeS: LIneS In tHe SAnD\n\n345", "source_file": "Lean_Analytics.pdf", "extraction_method": "pdfminer", "ocr_used": false, "has_table": false, "chapter_num": "26", "chapter_title": "USer-generAteD Content: LIneS In tHe SAnD", "section_num": null, "section_title": null, "l1_summary": "Unlike a traditional e-commerce company, you don’t have a lot of control\nover inventory and listings. But what you do have is insight into what is\nselling well, so you can go and get more like it. If you find that a particular\nproduct category, geographic region, house size, or color is selling...", "l2_summary": "Unlike a traditional e-commerce company, you don’t have a lot of control\nover inventory and listings. But what you do have is insight into what is\nselling well, so you can go and get more like it. If you find that a particular\nproduct category, geographic region, house size, or color is selling well, you\ncan encourage those sellers---and find more like them. CHAPter 27: two-SIDeD MArKetPLACeS: LIneS In tHe SAnD", "prev_page": {"page_num": 370, "segment_id": "00370"}, "next_page": {"page_num": 372, "segment_id": "00372"}, "extended_fields": {"has_code": false, "has_formulas": false, "has_diagram": false, "has_list": false, "has_citations": false, "key_terms": ["have", "what", "selling", "well", "more", "like", "find"], "content_type": "theory", "domain": "management|other", "complexity": "intermediate", "companies": [], "people": [], "products": ["product category", "geographic region", "house size", "color"], "tec